title: 123: You are What You Digest with Naveen Jain
description:
How do you optimize your brain health? Specifically, what kind of food can you eat for your brain?

What you eat matters for your gray matter. But here’s the thing. What’s good for one person is not necessarily good for the other person.

I’m excited about our conversation today with Naveen Jain. He is an entrepreneur and philanthropist driven to solve the world's biggest challenges through innovation. The founder of Moon Express, World Innovation Institute, iNome, TalentWise, Intelius, and Infospace, Naveen sees beyond the current business and technological landscape, creating companies that make a real impact.

In this episode, we’re going to share with you a powerful tool that can help you measure and optimize the health of your brain.

** Do you want to stay up to date with every new episode and get my brand new Kwik Brain Accelerator Program? Go to www.KwikBrain.com/podcast to get instant access. **
